query:
SELECT stationKey, COUNT(*) as count
FROM tmlReadings
WHERE inspectionId IN (SELECT id FROM inspections WHERE vesselTagNumber = '54-11-001')
GROUP BY stationKey
HAVING count > 1
ORDER BY count DESC;
